        "text_block_R8G3QC": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "title_heading": false,
            "accordion_enabled": false,
            "text": "<h4>Sustainable UPF Swimwear for Women Who Live in the Water</h4><p>At Ocean Soul Swimwear, we create more than just beautiful swimwear – we create functional pieces that empower women to feel confident, protected, and aligned with their values. Our sustainable UPF swimwear combines flattering silhouettes with eco-conscious innovation, so you never have to choose between style, performance, or sustainability.</p><p></p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
            "accordion_icon_size": 20
          }
        },
        "text_block_FRY9qz": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "title_heading": false,
            "accordion_enabled": false,
            "text": "<p>Crafted from luxurious Italian recycled fabric, every swimsuit offers UPF 50+ sun protection, resisting the damaging effects of UV rays while feeling soft and sculpting against your skin. Whether you're surfing, freediving, swimming laps, or chasing little ones along the shore, our suits are built to stay on, move with you, and hold their shape over time.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
            "accordion_icon_size": 20
          }
        },
        "text_block_hLGNdK": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "title_heading": false,
            "accordion_enabled": false,
            "text": "<p>Each design features thoughtful panel placement to enhance your natural curves, seamless finishes for all-day comfort, and a cinched waistband to define the waistline. Our sustainable UPF one pieces and bikinis are double-lined, so there’s no need for bulky padding – just smart construction and elevated design that holds and supports you in all the right places.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
            "accordion_icon_size": 20
          }
        },
        "text_block_nji8zx": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "title_heading": false,
            "accordion_enabled": false,
            "text": "<p>This is sustainable UPF swimwear made for active women who care about what they wear and where it comes from. All pieces are ethically manufactured in Bali with fair wages and a low-impact production process. From surf-friendly long sleeves to sleek one pieces and seamless bikinis, every piece reflects our commitment to protecting both your skin and the planet.</p><p><strong>Feel good in your swimwear – and even better about the impact you're making.</strong></p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
            "accordion_icon_size": 20
          }
        }
      },
