    "image_with_text_mXLPM3": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/black_upf_lomg_sleeve_swimsuit_sulawesi_ocean_soul_swimwear.jpg",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 550,
        "mobile_image_height": 300,
        "title": "",
        "text": "<h2>ULTIMATE SUN PROTECTION</h2><p>Crafted from luxurious Italian recycled fabrics, all Ocean Soul pieces offer UPF 50+ protection, sculpting shapes, and a stay-put fit designed for surf, swim, and everything in between. Whether you're after long sleeve bathers that flatter and shield you from the sun, or a minimalist two piece swimwear set for your next ocean adventure, you’ll find something here that feels like it was made just for you.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_CrgWyt": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Caragh_s_Edits_-_Mentawai_Celestial_Blue_March_2025-2_copy.jpg",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 550,
        "mobile_image_height": 300,
        "title": "",
        "text": "<h2>Made from Eco-Friendly Recycled Materials</h2><p>Sustainability is at the heart of everything we do. Our suits are crafted from Econyl®, a regenerated nylon made from ocean waste like fishing nets, fabric scraps, and industrial plastic. This fabric feels incredibly soft, smooth, and breathable, yet is strong enough to hold its shape through repeated wears and washes.</p><p>Ocean Soul’s sustainable swimwear is designed to last twice as long as conventional suits, so you can reduce consumption without compromising quality. It’s about choosing better – for your body and the earth.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_mmwV6x": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Blue-10_georgina_monti_by_izziephotographs_1.jpg",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 550,
        "mobile_image_height": 300,
        "title": "",
        "text": "<h2>Designed for Active Movement</h2><p>We know how frustrating it is when swimwear doesn't perform. That’s why every piece in our sustainable UPF swimwear collection is built for support, comfort, and security in motion. Whether you're duck diving under waves or diving deep into the blue, our swimsuits stay put and never sag. </p><p>We use clever design techniques:</p><p>That define and hold</p><p>To contour the body</p><p>To prevent digging or discomfort<br/> that flatters without bulk</p><p>The result? A suit that feels like it was made just for you – secure, flattering, and freedom-enhancing.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
