            "rating": 5,
            "title": "Quality and Style",
            "text": "<p>Timeless suits of the highest quality. I cannot rate this company enough - including their personal service and speedy dispatch. As someone who feels hugely conscious about her body in swimwear, I have never felt as confident and received so many compliments. Thank you, Ocean Soul. My fourth purchase and I don’t think I’ll ever shop for bathers anywhere else again!</p>",
