            "image": "shopify://shop_images/045A1973.jpg",
            "rating": 5,
            "title": "My favourite one piece!",
            "text": "<p>I ordered this one-piece swimsuit for freediving and I am delighted with it. Since I have been wearing it, I have felt much less cold during my sessions. The resistance of its materials, its sexy cut, its comfort outside and in the water, its anti-UV protection make it a simply perfect and essential accessory. I can only recommend it !</p>",
