          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "shipping_outline",
            "text": "Ultimate Sun Protection, NaturallyOur swimwear is made with UPF 50+ fabric, providing the highest level of protection against harmful UV rays. Unlike sunscreen that wears off in the water, UPF swimwear offers consistent sun protection that never needs to be reapplied. It's the perfect choice for surfers, swimmers, paddleboarders, and anyone spending hours under the sun.By choosing UPF sustainable swimwear, you're not only shielding your skin but reducing your need for chemical sunscreens – a win for your health and the ocean.",
